M||titl|Use SWR for Automatic Deduplication
M||impa|md-hi
M||impa|automatic deduplication
M||tags|client, swr, deduplication, data-fetching
M||tx|---
M|Use |tx|SWR enables request deduplication, caching, and revalidation across cp instances.
M|Use |**In|**
M|Use |tx|```tsx
M|Use |tx|fn UserList() {
M|Use |tx|const [us, setUsers] = useState([])
M|Use |tx|useEffect(() => {
M|Use |tx|fetch('/ap/us')
M|Use |tx|.then(r => r.json())
M|Use |tx|.then(setUsers)
M|Use |tx|}, [])
M|Use |tx|}
M|Use |tx|```
M|Use |**Co|**
M|Use |tx|```tsx
M|Use |tx|import useSWR from 'swr'
M|Use |tx|fn UserList() {
M|Use |cons|us } = useSWR('/ap/us', fetcher)
M|Use |tx|}
M|Use |tx|```
M|Use |**Fo|**
M|Use |tx|```tsx
M|Use |tx|import { useImmutableSWR } from '@/lib/swr'
M|Use |tx|fn StaticContent() {
M|Use |tx|const { data } = useImmutableSWR('/ap/config', fetcher)
M|Use |tx|}
M|Use |tx|```
M|Use |**Fo|**
M|Use |tx|```tsx
M|Use |tx|import { useSWRMutation } from 'swr/mutation'
M|Use |tx|fn UpdateButton() {
